dc_title_s: Prishtina, hartë e qytetit 1:10 000 : hartë rrugore dhe turistike : hartë e qytetit 1:10 000 = Prishtina, city map 1:8 000 : road and touristic map : city map 1:10 000
dc_description_s: General-content street map showing principal buildings and generalized land use. Panel title. Includes note, street index, and airline advertisements. Includes: Regional map of city "Monumente kulturoro-historike dhe natyrore = Cultural-historical and natural monuments" with legend, city panoramic photograph, color illustrations on recto and verso. Text, regional map of city "Monumente kulturoro-historike dhe natyrore = Cultural-historical and natural monuments" with legend, panoramic photographic color illustrations of the city, and other color illustrations on verso.
